有了进步，跟他们的交谈也让其了解了教材整体设计的重要意义。 公开信息显示，吴勇，毕业于中央工艺美术学院（现清华大学美术学院）装潢系书籍装帧专业。他曾为汕头大学长江艺术与设计学院视觉传达专业主任、教授、硕士生导师。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-2ae78415a8debcd4971cced243c377ea_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/534798528"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIxu2si5LavfonEAMaCDgxMTI2MDg1IIeswZQGMAM4lQJAFHIJNTM0Nzk4NTI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1653697896.5353162", "card_id": "Q_534696357", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "阿里巴巴 2022 财年第四季度营收 2040.5 亿元，净利润 198 亿元，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "阿里巴巴集团 5 月 26 日发布 2022 财年第四季度（2022 年 1-3 月）报告。第四财季营收 2040.5 亿元，同比增长 8.9%，预估 2005.9 亿元；第四财季调整后每 ADS 收益 7.95 元，预估 7.10 元。调整后净利润 198.0 亿元人民币，同比下降 24%。调整后息税折旧及摊销前利润 233.7 亿元，同比下降 22%，预估 220.3 亿元。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f7c1927f84fa606416c737334c082905_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/534696357"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ixu2si5LavfonEAMaCDgxMTAzMzA0II/JvZQGMA44rQNAFXIJNTM0Njk2MzU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1653697896.5359437", "card_id": "Q_534157828", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 224}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "男生都喜欢甜妹吗？像王心凌那样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近王心凌实红，除了老梗支持心 0 有 1 靠，现在中年男粉都去买芒果股票了。还有花泽香菜演唱会，近万宅男整齐划一跟唱，甜妹的力量这么强大的吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-2870050f5b1b0c182f0ef0b57831c26d_1440w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type"